name: Inside the Positronic Brain
description: Artwork for EP "INSIDE THE POSITRONIC BRAIN" by the Curitiba-based electronic music producer STANCKE (www.soundcloud.com/stancke). The artwork took inspiration from sci-fi movies, animes and HQ art based on the concept of artificial intelligence, cyborg/robots and hyper-humanism. The EP's name comes from the concept of positronic brain and the three laws of robotics, originally created by the sci-fi writer Isaac Asimov. Listen to the full album: https://bit.ly/3fPNIZN.
